{"tid":701993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗梁逸朗:《大香港早晨》作為本台皇牌時政節目 平均16萬收視","createTime":"2018-06-14T14:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T07:59:41.000Z","uid":157483,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd4f34e8510670ca6007257988097f70230f550b","tid":701993,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"【逸朗：《大香港早晨》的威力 &mdash; 收視證明一切】<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「熱血時報威力大」，而《大香港早晨》作為本台皇牌時政節目，其影響力更是不容小覷。老闆曾公布《大香港早晨》的收視人數，原來每集節目平均有達16萬個用戶點擊收看，成績驚人。若大家對16萬這個數字沒甚麼概念，可參考以下數據作比較：<br />\n<br />\n據香港電台2011年公布的數字，《千禧年代》的收聽人數平均介乎於13萬至23萬；《自由風自由phone》的收聽人數則介乎於7萬至13萬。據尼爾森收視調查，去年5月，ViuTV於黃金時段的平均收視為2.1點，即有約13萬6千人收看。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，《大香港早晨》的觀眾量，已能媲美，甚至是超越主流媒體。<br />\n<br />\n猶記得我首次亮相熱血時報後，已馬上感受到這個平台的威力。2014年9月，我甫做完我《大香港早晨》的處女作，即見少女Joey已揚言要為我成立Fans Club；幾天後，我更有幸在路上被觀眾認出。突然上升的知名度，對我來說，固然是驚喜，但同時也是警醒。因為主持一個觀眾群如此龐大的節目，我在節目中的表現，都會被十多萬人看在眼內。而我所傳播的訊息，亦有可能左右公眾輿論走向。因此，我要時刻提醒自己，主持《大香港早晨》不能馬虎，除了不能辜負觀眾的期望，更要肩負起傳訊的使命，宣揚我們堅信的理念，並令新媒體得以繼續茁壯成長。"},{"pid":"3c09bc5ad63d0df7a3135172ce100e6cb928aa94","tid":701993,"uid":188887,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"16 萬人聽都無4000人訂收費台又係咩概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8b081413573c2db8a0c40cbdfbb4f6eccf4c8b","tid":701993,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c09bc5ad63d0df7a3135172ce100e6cb928aa94","tid":701993,"uid":188887,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"16 萬人聽都無4000人訂收費台又係咩概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa032bc025f311d53b86bb8bf108f96c68c16c0","tid":701993,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"吹水既威力大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6a70405aea0a2e0e8700612faa5e98e333e634","tid":701993,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"佢係咪坐緊監？"},{"pid":"819c236489973ae7dfbce255342459be9b115b60","tid":701993,"uid":72730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"「我所傳播的訊息，亦有可能左右公眾輿論走向」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/010846_d6936733251a779ca46b80b072080e9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F010846_d6936733251a779ca46b80b072080e9f.jpg&h=f17bb69a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f16d0d4fe6a52c25a75faac5b86aa1c6a3309749","tid":701993,"uid":112416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:59:47.000Z","msg":"咁巴閉就直接搵尼爾森幫自己做一次收視調查啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf72990f5845ac0e0120ce4d94895b011436116","tid":701993,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"1600都唔知有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab628fc8fa96f6b861984845a7317d3d596355d","tid":701993,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf72990f5845ac0e0120ce4d94895b011436116","tid":701993,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"1600都唔知有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"160都唔知有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314a0a4e59fd04e65aea14cecfa2ca28a2b595fc","tid":701993,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ab628fc8fa96f6b861984845a7317d3d596355d","tid":701993,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf72990f5845ac0e0120ce4d94895b011436116","tid":701993,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"1600都唔知有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"160都唔知有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"全盛時期平均應該有幾千人<br />\n過萬就可能嚮雨革嗰期會有<br />\n平時就無咩可能<br />\n而家應該得返幾百人<br />\n我估300人左右"},{"pid":"b78d6cae618441dc121b78974f3158853c42984d","tid":701993,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"肯定計錯數，700萬人口起碼有300萬收睇"}]}